FOOTBALL: Netherly picks up 12th offer, gets calls from Texas A&M, Arizona State By Joshua Koch jkoch@hcnonline.com Houston Community Newspapers 
In a big game week for Crosby, Cougars junior wide receiver Emmanuel Netherly had a big night personally on Wednesday. 
Netherly has been continuously picking up offers throughout the season and on Wednesday added two more. God is Good just received my 12th offer from the university Texas A&M #GigEm üôè pic.twitter.com/x4G3ZCK79Q ‚Äî Emmanuel Netherly (@yovng_netherly) October 22, 2015 
With the addition of Texas A&M and Arizona State to his list on Wednesday, Netherly now has 12 offers. 
Netherly has racked up 740 yards and 12 touchdowns this season for the Cougars. Blessed to receive my 11th offer from Arizona State University #ForksUp üôè.! pic.twitter.com/MPTDJVgY4p ‚Äî Emmanuel Netherly (@yovng_netherly) October 22, 2015
